OL,3,CLEGO fans divided by new 'smart' bricks
OL,5,FLEGO has launched 'smart' bricks,
OL,6,Fwhich are tech-filled versions of
OL,7,Ftheir normal building blocks, but fans
OL,8,Fare divided as to whether it's a good
OL,9,Fidea.
OL,11,FThere are three parts of the new
OL,12,Fsystem that work together - the smart
OL,13,Fbrick, smart tags which tell the brick
OL,14,Fwhat to do, and smart minifigures,
OL,15,Fwhich react to their environment with
OL,16,Fsounds, moods and reactions.
