OL,3,CLEGO fans divided by new 'smart' bricks
OL,5,FLEGO has called the new system its
OL,6,F"most revolutionary innovation since
OL,7,Fthe creation of the minifigure in
OL,8,F1978", saying it should "help (LEGO)
OL,9,Fplay back with you".
OL,11,FBut LEGO fans have had mixed responses
OL,12,Fto the upgraded bricks.
