OL,3,CLEGO fans divided by new 'smart' bricks
OL,5,FLEGO content creator @emmasaurus wrote
OL,6,Fthat the new bricks were "exciting",
OL,7,Fbut creator @digging for bricks was
OL,8,Fcritical of the new bricks.
OL,10,F"This is obviously a play feature," he
OL,11,Fposted on Instagram.
OL,13,F"You know who loves play features,
OL,14,F(that's) kids. Do you know who does
OL,15,Fnot have $150 to spend on a set? Kids.
OL,16,FDo you know who does? Adults. Do you
OL,17,Fknow what adults do with their LEGO?
OL,18,FThey put them on display shelves, and
OL,19,Fthey don't use the play features."
