OL,3,CLEGO fans divided by new 'smart' bricks
OL,5,FHe also criticised changing something
OL,6,Fthat has typically offered escapism
OL,7,Ffrom technology.
OL,9,F"I am tired of technology being
OL,10,Fintroduced into every single thing in
OL,11,Flife. I build LEGO to take a break
OL,12,Ffrom technology and get away from
OL,13,Ftechnology."
OL,15,FOther comments suggest the new tech
OL,16,Ftakes away some of the element of
OL,17,Fimagination that makes LEGO fun, but
OL,18,Fthe company said that wasn't the case,
OL,19,Fposting: "Still absolutely vital!
OL,20,FImagination will always be key in
OL,21,Fcreating your own stories."
