OL,3,CLEGO fans divided by new 'smart' bricks
OL,5,FThe company also refuted a suggestion
OL,6,Fthat artificial intelligence would be
OL,7,Finvolved, writing: "No AI here! Just
OL,8,Fsuper SMART tech."
OL,10,FTom Donaldson, Senior Vice President &
OL,11,FHead of Creative Play Lab at the LEGO
OL,12,FGroup, has said the launch "brings
OL,13,Fcreativity, technology and
OL,14,Fstorytelling together", and emphasised
OL,15,Fthe new tech is still "without a
OL,16,Fscreen".
