OL,3,CLEGO fans divided by new 'smart' bricks
OL,5,F"We truly believe we are setting a new
OL,6,Fstandard for interactive, imaginative
OL,7,Fexperiences and can't wait to see this
OL,8,Finnovation in the hands of kids when
OL,9,Fwe launch this year," he added.
OL,11,FLEGO was created by the Kirk
OL,12,FKristiansen family in 1932 in Denmark,
OL,13,Fand the standard LEGO brick in its
OL,14,Fcurrent form was launched in 1958.
OL,16,FThe first smart play sets will be
OL,17,Flaunched in March and will be part of
OL,18,Fthe LEGO Star Wars series.
